1. *Odlazite* danas? (Are you leaving today?)
2. Tvoji prijatelji *odlaze* u grad? (Are your friends leaving for the city?)
3. Šta *odlazi*? (What is leaving?)
4. Nisam mogao da sprečim da se *odlazi*. (I couldn't stop from leaving.)
5. Mi *odlazimo* prekosutra. (We are leaving the day after tomorrow.)